title: Grateful Dead Live at Paramount Northwest Theater on 1977-09-29
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half-Step Uptown Toodeloo, Mama Tried, Deal, Looks Like Rain, Ramble On Rose, El Paso, Sugaree, Let It Grow, Franklin's Tower

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Estimated Prophet-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Stella Blue-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Johnny B. Goode, E: Uncle John's Band
